00:16:17,210 --> 00:16:20,350
Agent Han Tae Kyung má VIP.

120
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:45,880
<i>Ukradl sanitku. SPZ 9337. </i>

121
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:48,660
